  "Two teams are in a deadlock over budget allocation. You want to find middle ground.": "/audio/carlos-vinicius-vale-bassan/aula6_oral_3_situation.mp3",
  "Someone makes an argument you partially agree with. You want to concede some points while maintaining your position.": "/audio/carlos-vinicius-vale-bassan/aula6_oral_4_situation.mp3",
  "A client is unhappy with your proposal. You need to acknowledge their concerns and persuade them.": "/audio/carlos-vinicius-vale-bassan/aula6_oral_5_situation.mp3",
  "Your team wants to take a conservative approach but you believe a bolder strategy is needed. You must persuade them.": "/audio/carlos-vinicius-vale-bassan/aula6_oral_6_situation.mp3",
  "I see your point, but I would argue that the data supports a different approach. Would it be fair to say we look at the numbers together?": "/audio/carlos-vinicius-vale-bassan/aula6_oral_1_model.mp3",
  "I acknowledge the potential benefits of this plan, however, I am not entirely convinced about the timeline. Can we justify the assumptions behind it?": "/audio/carlos-vinicius-vale-bassan/aula6_oral_2_model.mp3",
